{
  "phoneNumber":"9842114259"
}

### Update Dealer
PATCH http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/vehicle-management/Dealers('D001')
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status":"INACTIVE"
}

### Update Vehicle Status
PATCH http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/vehicle-management/Vehicles('TN1001')
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleStatus":"RESERVED"
}

#########################
### Update Vehicle Status
